name: iqgeek
overview: IQGEEK” an on demand computer support created with the vision and resolution to enhance your computing experience. With stamped presence in several regions and efficient manpower we are here to maneuver your cyber problems. Today in this fast paced world we can’t really wait for a “Geek” to come in, at time when remote support has changed the way support was being delivered. The local geeks demand your presence which in a way is time consuming and lethargic at the same time. Now in this frame the Team GOD (geeks on duty) formed by IQGEEK will transform the way computer services were being delivered. By raising the precision level and setting up benchmark for generations to follow and admire using the latest technology of remote support, patented software and one to one interaction. Team GOD believes in the Greek word “Citius” which means faster with accuracy and precision. Team GOD being versatile provides all kinds of computer related services “under one roof” called IQGEEK. • We provide support to all major brands of “computers and laptops”. • We provide instantaneous Email Support so as to ensure no interference in your day to day communication. • Team GOD masters in providing Microsoft Support with unprecedented expertise. • We maximize your antivirus performance with our Antivirus Support to guard you against all odds. • Browser bridges you to the internet and our Browser Support would ensure that the “bridge is well optimized”. • Team God printer and scanner support ensures your devices are up and running always.
